- decisions: slug `panhandle-garage-door-company`; FULL build (richness 10); real WordPress on Surface via Docker+Flask bridge; SEO analyzer must allow account creation with any fake email/password and run live after deploy; bespoke door-company design, not portfolio look.
- next needs: intake → brief.json must capture all technical-SEO line items, 8 service silos, Panhandle geography, "One Company. Every Door.", and the open-signup analyzer requirement as gradable requirements.
- risks: WP-Docker-on-Surface fragility (pull timeout, sub-path login, canonical loops); open-signup auth compatibility; dual-backend port/service management.
